high_descs: Turn left and go forward, then turn left to go to the fridge, then turn right and move forward, then turn left to face the dishwasher.
Pick up the egg from the counter in front of you.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Wash the egg in the sink.
Turn around and go to the stove, then look up to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the egg inside, then close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean egg in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter to the right of the fridge where the toaster is.
Pick up the egg that is on the counter that is surrounded by three knives and between the two heads of lettuce.
With the egg in hand turn and go to the sink.
Place the egg in the sink to the left of the spatula and in front of the plate. Turn the water on to wash the egg.  Turn the water off and pick up the egg.
With the egg in hand turn and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the egg to the left of the egg that is in the microwave.  Shut the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Wash an egg and put it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the fridge, then take a couple steps to the right. Face the counter.
Pick up the egg on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Wash the egg in the sink.
Turn around and veer right to the stove and microwave.
Place the egg in the microwave, near the middle.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed egg in a microwave.
